OL,3,C'Revolutionary' device to tackle acid
OL,4,Creflux given to first UK patients
OL,6,FA 30-year-old has said her 'symptoms
OL,7,Fhave completely disappeared' after
OL,8,Fbecoming the first patient to undergo
OL,9,Fa 'revolutionary' procedure to treat
OL,10,Fsevere acid reflux, ITV News Reporter
OL,11,FOlivia Guthrie reports.
OL,13,FA "revolutionary" method to treat
OL,14,Fsevere acid reflux has been implanted
OL,15,Fin patients for the first time, which
OL,16,Fcould help tackle an issue that
OL,17,Fimpacts 20% of the UK's adult
OL,18,Fpopulation.
