OL,3,C'Revolutionary' device to tackle acid
OL,4,Creflux given to first UK patients
OL,6,FUniversity Hospital Southampton (UHS)
OL,7,Fand Imperial College London have
OL,8,Fbecome the first NHS trusts in the
OL,9,Fcountry to install the device called
OL,10,Fthe RefluxStop, with Southampton being
OL,11,Fthe first to use robotic surgery for
OL,12,Fthe procedure.
OL,14,FKnown as gastro-oesophageal reflux
OL,15,Fdisease (GORD), the condition occurs
OL,16,Fwhen contents from the stomach flow
OL,17,Fback into the oesophagus ` the long
OL,18,Ftube that carries food from the throat
OL,19,Fto the stomach.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
