OL,3,C'Revolutionary' device to tackle acid
OL,4,Creflux given to first UK patients
OL,6,FRefluxStop is fixed to the upper part
OL,7,Fof the stomach wall and blocks
OL,8,Fmovement of the lower oesophageal
OL,9,Fsphincter to hold it in its original,
OL,10,Fnatural position and restore normal
OL,11,Fanatomy and function.
OL,13,FMade out of medical grade rounded
OL,14,Fsolid silicone, the implant measures
OL,15,Faround 25mm ` smaller than a ping pong
OL,16,Fball ` and is fitted via robotic-
OL,17,Fassisted laparoscopic (keyhole)
OL,18,Fsurgery as a day case, with patients
OL,19,Fin theatre for less than two hours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
