OL,3,C'Revolutionary' device to tackle acid
OL,4,Creflux given to first UK patients
OL,6,FA UHS spokeswoman said that
OL,7,Fapproximately 20% of the adult UK
OL,8,Fpopulation have problems with severe
OL,9,Facid reflux or GORD and UHS treats
OL,10,Fabout 50 patients every year with the
OL,11,Fcondition.
OL,13,FThe disease can also lead to further
OL,14,Fcomplications such as oesophageal
OL,15,Fulcers, a scarred and narrow
OL,16,Foesophagus, Barrett's oesophagus `
OL,17,Fchanges to the cells in the lining of
OL,18,Fthe oesophagus ` and oesophageal
OL,19,Fcancer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
