OL,3,C'Revolutionary' device to tackle acid
OL,4,Creflux given to first UK patients
OL,6,FIt is estimated that one in every 10
OL,7,Fto 20 people with Barrett's oesophagus
OL,8,Fwill develop oesophageal cancer within
OL,9,F10 to 20 years.
OL,11,FDanielle Harding, 30, recently became
OL,12,Fthe first patient with GORD to undergo
OL,13,Fthe procedure at UHS.
OL,15,FThe mother-of-two, from Southampton,
OL,16,Fsaid: "I began suffering with severe
OL,17,Facid reflux in 2022 and it has
OL,18,Faffected my life in so many ways `
OL,19,Fanything that involves eating or
OL,20,Fdrinking has caused me so much
OL,21,Fanxiety, especially outside of my home.
