OL,3,C'Revolutionary' device to tackle acid
OL,4,Creflux given to first UK patients
OL,6,F"The signs are almost immediate with
OL,7,Fan intense pain in my chest as the
OL,8,Freflux comes up the oesophagus and
OL,9,Fburns my throat, often resulting in me
OL,10,Fvomiting, it's been horrendous."
OL,12,FMs Harding was prescribed medication
OL,13,Ffrom her GP which initially stopped
OL,14,Fthe symptoms only for them to return.
OL,16,FAn endoscopy showed that she had
OL,17,Fsignificant damage to her oesophagus
OL,18,Fand that she would need to remain on a
OL,19,Fhigh dose of medication for life.
