OL,3,C'Revolutionary' device to tackle acid
OL,4,Creflux given to first UK patients
OL,6,FMs Harding said the RefluxStop was a
OL,7,F"no-brainer" for her and added: "I had
OL,8,Fthe surgery a little over a month ago
OL,9,Fand my symptoms have completely
OL,10,Fdisappeared.
OL,12,FFergus Noble, consultant general and
OL,13,Foesophagogastric surgeon at UHS, said:
OL,14,F"RefluxStop is revolutionary in that
OL,15,Fit is minimally invasive, restores the
OL,16,Flower oesophageal valve to its natural
OL,17,Fposition with no side effects and
OL,18,Foffers some patients a viable
OL,19,Ftreatment option for the first time."
